<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Teamwork Cares recently participated in the Pack-A-Snack event at HOB Brewing Company in Dunedin, Florida. Volunteers gathered to contribute snacks, which were then assembled into care packages for distribution to children in need.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">The Pack-A-Snack program is designed to provide nutritious weekend snacks to children facing food insecurity in the greater Dunedin area. Schools identify students who are most in need, ensuring they receive a bag of healthy, pre-packaged snacks each Friday afternoon.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Teamwork Cares, the volunteer initiative of Teamwork Commerce, harnesses the company's global reach and diverse workforce to support programs that foster education, mentorship, and community well-being worldwide.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">We are proud to contribute to our community and are grateful for the opportunity to make a positive impact.</p>
